This app will take the input of what your paycheck amout is divide the amount in a 50-30-20 rule

50% being what NEEDS to be spent every month:
rent, gas/electric, creditcard, groceries, bus pass, internet, phone

30% goes to WANTS:
subscriptions(TV, panera, blw), dinners, fast food, clothes

20% goes to savungs:
5%- Emergency fund
5%- HSA health savings account
5%- Investments
5%- Big purchases

with the added ability to calculate what the savings would be if you started from/to a previous/future


